== Spanish ==
===Etymology===
Latin ''[[quaerere|quaerĕre]]''

=== Verb ===
'''querer'''

# to [[desire]]; to [[want]]
# to [[love]]; to be [[fond]] of
# (''an indication of a request'')
#: ''¿Quieres decirme que pasa?'' - "Would you tell me what happened?"
'''querer decir'''
# to [[mean]]
'''sin querer'''
# to do something unintentionally

